  "Description": {
    "English": "A consumable liquid, created in the <span class=\"name name-technology\">Nutrient Processor</span>.  Prized across the galaxy for its pleasing mouth-feel and authentically natural flavours.<br><br><br>Can be ingested as it stands or subjected to further processing.",
    "SimplifiedChinese": "通过<span class=\"name name-technology\">营养处理器</span>制作的可饮用液体。因其柔顺的口感和真实的天然风味，在星系中备受赞誉。<br><br>可直接饮用或进一步加工。",
    "TencentChinese": "通过<span class=\"name name-technology\">营养处理器</span>制作的可饮用液体。<br><br>可直接饮用或留作进一步处理。",
    "TraditionalChinese": "消耗性液體，<span class=\"name name-technology\">營養處理器的產物。</span>極佳的口感和真正天然的香味可以說是銀河系的珍饈。<br><br>可直接飲用或進行後續處理。"
  },
